A11yPermission.checkBoxText: E-ea ka kotloloho ho ea lumellang pele ho halofo ea khoeli le ho se hlotsoe fensetere ena
A11yPermission.content: Ts'ebetso ena e hloka tumello ea ts'ebetso ea mosebetsi. Haeba u batla ho lumelisa, ka kopo tlanya [ho lokile]. Haeba u batla ho tela, ka kopo tlanya [ho hlakola]
A11yPermission.title: Sesebelisoa sa tumello

floatPermission.checkBoxText: E-ea ka kotloloho ho ea lumellang pele ho halofo ea khoeli le ho se hlotsoe fensetere ena
floatPermission.content: Ts'ebetso ena e hloka tumello ea ts'ebetso ea fensetere ea ho phaphamala. Haeba u batla ho lumelisa, ka kopo tlanya [ho lokile]. Haeba u batla ho tela, ka kopo tlanya [ho hlakola]
